blon|San&nbsp;Fernando]]\n| {{percent and number|23,271|292,781|disp=table|1|pad=yes}}\n| 22,466\n| {{PAGR|color=true|2015.5835|23,271|2010.3315|22,466}}\n| {{convert|196.87|km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| {{convert|{{sigfig|23,271/196.87|2}}|PD/km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 12\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"border-right:0;background-color:initial;\" | {{coord|12.0610|N|121.9594|E|name=San Jose|region:PH-ROM_type:city|format=hidden}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;font-weight:bold;border-left:0;\" colspan=\"2\" | [[San Jose, Romblon|San&nbsp;Jose]]\n| {{percent and number|10,881|292,781|disp=table|1|pad=yes}}\n| 10,294\n| {{PAGR|color=true|2015.5835|10,881|2010.3315|10,294}}\n| {{convert|22.05|km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| {{convert|{{sigfig|10,881/22.05|2}}|PD/km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 5\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"border-right:0;background-color:initial;\" | {{coord|12.1552|N|121.9943|E|name=Santa Fe|region:PH-ROM_type:city|format=hidden}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;font-weight:bold;border-left:0;\" colspan=\"2\" | [[Santa Fe, Romblon|Santa&nbsp;Fe]]\n| {{percent and number|16,098|292,781|disp=table|1|pad=yes}}\n| 15,700\n| {{PAGR|color=true|2015.5835|16,098|2010.3315|15,700}}\n| {{convert|63.52|km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| {{convert|{{sigfig|16,098/63.52|2}}|PD/km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 11\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"border-right:0;background-color:initial;\" | {{coord|12.3938|N|122.0938|E|name=Santa Maria|region:PH-ROM_type:city|format=hidden}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;font-weight:bold;border-left:0;\" colspan=\"2\" | [[Santa Maria, Romblon|Santa Maria]]&nbsp;{{small|(''Imelda'')}}\n| {{percent and number|8,508|292,781|disp=table|1|pad=yes}}\n| 7,683\n| {{PAGR|color=true|2015.5835|8,508|2010.3315|7,683}}\n| {{convert|36.20|km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| {{convert|{{sigfig|8,508/36.20|2}}|PD/km2|abbr=values|disp=table}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 6\n|- class=\"sortbottom\"\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"border-right:0;\" |\n! colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-left:0;text-align:left;font-size:medium;font-variant:small-caps;letter-spacing:0.05em;\" | Total\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | 292,781\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | 283,930\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{PAGR|color=true|2015.5835|292,781|2010.3315|283,930}}\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | 1,533.45\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{convert|1,533.45|km2|disp=number|2}}\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{sigfig|292,781/1,533.45|2}}\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{convert|{{sigfig|292,781/1,533.45|2}}|PD/km2|disp=number}}\n! 219\n|- class=\"sortbottom\" style=\"background-color:#F2F2F2;line-height:1.3em;border-top:double grey;\"\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-width:thin 0 0 thin;\" |\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"border-width:thin 0 0 0;text-align:center;padding:0.7em 0;\" | {{Color box|white|\u2020|border=darkgray}}{{thinsp}}Provincial&nbsp;capital\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"border-width:thin 0 0 0;text-align:left;padding:0.7em 0;\" | {{Color box|white|border=darkgray}}{{thinsp}}Municipality\n|- class=\"sortbottom\" style=\"background-color:#F2F2F2;line-height:1.3em;font-size:110%;\"\n| colspan=\"13\" style=\"border-top:0;text-align:left;padding:0 13em;\" |\n{{notelist-lr|refs=\n{{efn-lr|name=FormerName|Former names are ''italicized''.}}\n{{efn-lr|name=Coord|The ''globe''&nbsp;[[File:WMA button2b.png|frameless|upright=0.1]] icon marks the [[town&nbsp;center]].}}\n}}\n|}\n{{col-break|gap=0.75em}}\n[[File:Ph fil romblon.png|thumb|upright=1.3|center|alt=Political divisions of Romblon]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Climate===\nRomblon falls under Type III of the Corona climatic classification system which was devised in 1920. It is characterized by no pronounced wet and dry seasons. Generally, the wet season is from June to November and sometimes extends up to December when the southwest monsoon is predominant. The dry season is from January to May but is sometimes interrupted by erratic rainfall. The annual mean temperature is {{convert|27|C|F}}, with February as the coldest month with temperatures dropping to {{convert|20|C|F}}, and May as the warmest month with temperatures reaching up to {{convert|35|C|F}}. ''[[Monsoon#Southwest monsoon|Habagat]]'' monsoon winds pass through the province from June to October while northeasterly winds or ''[[Amihan]]'' blows through the islands from December to February.<ref name=\"RomblonProv\"/><ref name=\"PSA\"/><ref name=\"MDG\"/>\n\n{{Weather box\n| location = Romblon, Romblon (1981\u20132010, extremes 1904\u20132012)\n| single line = Y\n| metric first = Y\n| temperature colour = pastel\n| Jan record high C = 35.5\n| Feb record high C = 35.1\n| Mar record high C = 35.8\n| Apr record high C = 37.5\n| May record high C = 38.2\n| Jun record high C = 38.2\n| Jul record high C = 37.7\n| Aug record high C = 35.7\n| Sep record high C = 35.8\n| Oct record high C = 35.3\n| Nov record high C = 35.2\n| Dec record high C = 34.1\n|year record high C = 38.2\n| Jan high C = 28.4\n| Feb high C = 29.1\n| Mar high C = 30.4\n| Apr high C = 32.0\n| May high C = 32.6\n| Jun high C = 31.7\n| Jul high C = 30.8\n| Aug high C = 30.5\n| Sep high C = 30.6\n| Oct high C = 30.3\n| Nov high C = 29.7\n| Dec high C = 28.5\n|year high C = 30.4\n| Jan mean C = 26.2\n| Feb mean C = 26.7\n| Mar mean C = 27.6\n| Apr mean C = 29.0\n| May mean C = 29.4\n| Jun mean C = 28.7\n| Jul mean C = 28.1\n| Aug mean C = 28.0\n| Sep mean C = 28.0\n| Oct mean C = 27.8\n| Nov mean C = 27.5\n| Dec mean C = 26.5\n|year mean C = 27.8\n| Jan low C = 24.0\n| Feb low C = 24.2\n| Mar low C = 24.9\n| Apr low C = 26.0\n| May low C = 26.3\n| Jun low C = 25.8\n| Jul low C = 25.4\n| Aug low C = 25.5\n| Sep low C = 25.3\n| Oct low C = 25.2\n| Nov low C = 25.2\n| Dec low C = 24.4\n|year low C = 25.2\n| Jan record low C = 18.4\n| Feb record low C = 17.0\n| Mar record low C = 19.7\n| Apr record low C = 20.1\n| May record low C = 15.6\n| Jun record low C = 20.